data.description: Welcome to The Elliot, a luxury boutique building of 3 residences constructed in 2019, that showcase contemporary interior design and supreme livability. This penthouse unit lives like a townhome with 3 spacious levels, generous room sizes, rear deck, and private off-street parking. The living areas of the home are drenched in natural light, boast lofty ceilings, and are excellent spaces for entertaining. Carrera quartz countertops are paired with deep espresso cabinetry for an eye-pleasing contrast in the kitchen that includes premium stainless steel appliances and island with room for seating. 1338 Fairmont St offers close proximity to the Columbia Heights & U Street Metro Stations, 14th St shopping & seasonal farmer’s market, Meridian Hill Park, coffee shops, & an incredible restaurant & bar scene - perfect for your modern urban lifestyle.
